sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant QP as Knative Activator /<br/>Queue Proxy<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant Caikit as Caikit Runtime<br/>(transformer container)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Models as /mnt/models/<br/>(shared volume)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus UWM<br/>8086/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,Models: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request
    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443 | TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    IstioGW->>QP: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8012 | mTLS STRICT | Istio PeerAuth
    QP->>Caikit: Forward to transformer<br/>HTTP/8080 | plaintext (in-pod)
    Caikit->>TGIS: Inference delegation<br/>gRPC/8033 | plaintext (localhost)
    TGIS->>Models: Read model weights<br/>File I/O
    Models-->>TGIS: Model tensors
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Generated text response
    Caikit-->>QP: JSON response
    QP-->>IstioGW: Response (mTLS)
    IstioGW-->>Client: JSON response (TLS)

    Note over Client,Models: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>IstioGW: gRPC NlpService.TextGeneration<br/>HTTPS(h2)/443 | TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    IstioGW->>QP: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8012 | mTLS STRICT | Istio PeerAuth
    QP->>Caikit: Forward to transformer<br/>gRPC(h2c)/8085 | plaintext (in-pod)
    Caikit->>TGIS: Inference delegation<br/>gRPC/8033 | plaintext (localhost)
    TGIS->>Models: Read model weights<br/>File I/O
    Models-->>TGIS: Model tensors
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Generated text (stream)
    Caikit-->>QP: gRPC response (stream)
    QP-->>IstioGW: Response (mTLS)
    IstioGW-->>Client: gRPC response (TLS)

    Note over Client,Models: Flow 3: Streaming Text Generation
    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/v1/task/server-streaming-text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443 | TLS 1.2+
    IstioGW->>QP: Forward (mTLS)
    QP->>Caikit: HTTP/8080 (in-pod)
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC stream/8033 (localhost)
    loop Token-by-token streaming
        TGIS-->>Caikit: Generated token
        Caikit-->>QP: SSE token
        QP-->>IstioGW: SSE token (mTLS)
        IstioGW-->>Client: SSE token (TLS)
    end

    Note over Prometheus,Caikit: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>Caikit: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086 | PERMISSIVE mTLS | No auth
    Caikit-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics

    Note over S3,Models: Flow 5: Model Loading (Init)
    Note right of S3: KServe storage initializer<br/>runs as init container
    S3-->>Models: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 | TLS 1.2+ | AWS IAM / S3 keys
